      {
        "question": "What confidence threshold is used?",
        "answer": "Only issues scoring 80 or higher are reported to minimize false positives."
      },
      {
        "question": "How does it integrate with GitHub?",
        "answer": "Uses GitHub CLI commands to fetch PR data and post comments when the --comment flag is provided."
      },
      {
        "question": "Is my code data safe?",
        "answer": "Yes - code is only processed locally through GitHub CLI and AI model context. No external data transfers."
